frames.caption: A cute, animated chick with large eyes and a purple scarf is joyfully holding a cupcake. The chick is sitting in a basket surrounded by colorful Easter eggs and butterflies fluttering around. The background is a softly blurred, sunlit garden setting.
frames.description: The scene depicts an adorable animated chick in a vibrant garden setting, enjoying a cupcake. The atmosphere is cheerful and whimsical, with butterflies adding to the lively ambiance.

frames.caption: A cute, fluffy yellow duckling wearing a purple scarf is joyfully holding a cupcake with white frosting. The scene is set in a whimsical outdoor environment with soft lighting and colorful butterflies fluttering around.
frames.description: The scene depicts a cheerful duckling in a vibrant, magical setting. The duckling is sitting on a wicker basket surrounded by colorful eggs and flowers, creating a playful and enchanting atmosphere.
